properties.DETAILS_PAGE_DESCRIPTION:
Columbia Beach Resort
Luxury, Leisure, and the Spirit of Play on Cyprus’s Southern Coast
Overlooking the tranquil waters of Pissouri Bay, Columbia Beach Resort is a five-star escape where Cypriot heritage meets refined luxury. With 169 elegant suites, award-winning spa treatments, two spectacular pools—including a signature infinity pool—and exceptional dining, the resort offers an unforgettable experience of relaxation and indulgence. For those with a passion for staying active, the resort features top-tier sports facilities, including a flood-lit tennis court, and a brand-new padel court. Whether you're a guest of the resort or visiting from outside, you're warmly welcome to enjoy the game and the stunning surroundings. All equipment is available for hire from the Hébe Spa Reception, so all you need to bring is your energy and enthusiasm.

properties.DETAILS_PAGE_DESCRIPTION:
Premium Padel Center is a modern indoor padel club located in Dali, Nicosia, right where the highways to Larnaca and Limassol branch off, easy to reach, no matter where you’re coming from.
Our club is open to everyone: from casual players who want to enjoy a fun game with friends, to beginners taking their first steps in padel, and competitive players looking to sharpen their skills in a focused environment.
We offer two fully indoor courts, so weather is never an issue. Before your match, you can warm up in our dedicated gym area, while friends and family can enjoy the action from our comfortable viewing gallery. We also provide modern changing rooms and showers for men and women, full wheelchair accessibility, and a welcoming atmosphere for all players.
Our courts are fully autonomous, giving you total freedom and flexibility. With a one-time password sent in your booking details, you can access the courts easily, no waiting, no queues, no staff dependency. Just arrive, enter, and play on your schedule.
At Premium Padel Center, it’s all about convenience, quality, and community, the perfect place to play padel your way.
For any further information, please contact us at +357 99 745001 or +357 97 797826
